 communiquer leurs intentions et leur vision du monde de façon détournée. Sont étudiées ici les œuvres de Patrick Chamoiseau (Martinique), Abdelkébir Khatibi (Maroc), Guy Tirolien (Guadeloupe), Werewere Liking (Cameroun), Marie NDiaye (France) et Cheikh Hamidou Kane (Sénégal). Sous la direction d'Amélie Michel avec la collaboration de Valeria Liljesthröm, Yasmina Sévigny-Côté, Maeva Archimède, Stéphanie Leclerc-Audet, Anne-Sophie Boudreau, Nicolas Treiber.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aFrench literaturezFrench-speaking countriesxHistory and criticism. 0aIntertextuality. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / Essays.2bisacsh1 aArchimède, Maëva, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAudet, Stéphanie Leclerc, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoudreau, Anne-Sophie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCôté, Yasmina Sévigny, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLiljesthröm, Valeria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichel, Amélie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichel, Amélie, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTreiber, Nicolas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763754222?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763754222423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763754222/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-a